{"tid":627982,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"借左財務公司錢好耐無還","createTime":"2018-04-13T12:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T07:36:43.000Z","uid":53209,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"865a754d7c6728ce9a8559cc78f0cb85a4f9f0a7","tid":627982,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:10:37.000Z","msg":"如題，我二叔 係2/30年前 借過邦文1皮野 走左數 到前排佢鳩痕痕走去開信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結果唔夠2個月就比人寄信追佢數 邦文好似已經揾左第間財仔追<br />\n<br />\n如果唔還，係咪搞破產就唔會再追? 破緊產個陣又會唔會繼續追數?<br />\n<br />\n如果還錢， 上邦文個到同佢傾，可以減到幾多到?(條數依加8萬銀)<br />\n<br />\n收數公司又會用咩手段追數?"},{"pid":"44f0b2b940ed07d314b823968a1b9e8cb05346ea","tid":627982,"uid":38253,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"叫你阿叔練下食飯飲湯唔好有聲先"},{"pid":"78fb10e6532ebc6901dc6162a8f6307af08eaf97","tid":627982,"uid":134128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:25:33.000Z","msg":"繼續借爆佢 之後申請破產"},{"pid":"06b1bf27f6b3cdc5554127e972d081005f167929","tid":627982,"uid":53209,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你阿叔練下食飯飲湯唔好有聲先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"26b810033bd6c857686c416ba3856f82967c78ca","tid":627982,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:40:32.000Z","msg":"三十萬。。收你8萬咪算小"},{"pid":"7f61404a200b89492939ff0317166a11e38e9b66","tid":627982,"uid":33886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26b810033bd6c857686c416ba3856f82967c78ca","tid":627982,"uid":33886,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:40:32.000Z","msg":"三十萬。。收你8萬咪算小"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:40:43.000Z","msg":"三十年*"},{"pid":"5be6e37aa4534dc5d0cda36625f1457933f9687c","tid":627982,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三十萬。。收你8萬咪算小</blockquote>三十年*</blockquote><br />\n我都覺 但依樣唔係重點"},{"pid":"deb4f9c73ee7eb76cc0ce25035b9f4519df2eb6c","tid":627982,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:01:16.000Z","msg":"推下 有無做緊財仔既巴打解答"},{"pid":"23e61dabbc69bcffea32691cb4822dbff33b4773","tid":627982,"uid":92936,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"要睇邦民係賣咗條數俾人定係純粹委託人地去追，如果係後者，破產係有用；如果係前者，就係睇下買果間公司係咪有牌財仔，無牌果啲話之你破產定破處都會照追 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條數唔大唔細，真係好睇追數果班點諗，佢地覺得值既咪上門兇下你；覺得唔值既咪打下電話寫下字之類，鎖門放火機會好微 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402c42990881c5dc74ba17b03568678cf321402b","tid":627982,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"咁多年8萬...<br />\n有冇咁好"},{"pid":"df56929c50bdd6409b232d8af839f19cb1d693a5","tid":627982,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f0b2b940ed07d314b823968a1b9e8cb05346ea","tid":627982,"uid":38253,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"叫你阿叔練下食飯飲湯唔好有聲先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ff7d2e350fc8e0ad24821931f28a35b45b8546","tid":627982,"uid":11862,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解開信用卡財仔會即刻知?"},{"pid":"c5bdc45cb58b843658f2b943b7f537baf1b64b0d","tid":627982,"uid":33059,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"你阿叔走左成三十年數，<br />\n你洗同佢擔心咩"},{"pid":"3bd702bcc1ab7d26973e9b6135c9e08fd7da2fa5","tid":627982,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要睇邦民係賣咗條數俾人定係純粹委託人地去追，如果係後者，破產係有用；如果係前者，就係睇下買果間公司係咪有牌財仔，無牌果啲話之你破產定破處都會照追 <img sr